ATRIAL RHYTHM MANAGEMENT FEATURES SUCH AS ATRIAL RATE STABILIZATION (ARS), ATRIAL PREFERENCE PACING (APP), AND POST MODE SWITCH OVERDRIVE PACING (PMOP) ARE INDICATED FOR THE SUPPRESSION OF ATRIAL TACHYARRHYTHMIAS IN ICD-INDICATED PATIENTS WITH ATRIAL SEPTAL LEAD PLACEMENT AND AN ICD INDICATION.
